sword_and_sorcery.title: Sword & Sorcery
sword_and_sorcery.description: Tales of legendary heroes, mythical beasts, and sorcery for those who can't get enough magic.

279425.title: Prince Killian And The Holy Grail
279425.description: A 12th-century knight-errant wanders the world fighting injustice and is accompanied by his faithful friends Crispin and Goliath.

286445.title: Merlin and the Book of Beasts
286445.description: In this fantasy thriller, an evil wizard terrorizes Camelot while a princess tries to persuade a bitter and broken Merlin to save their kingdom.

295882.title: Conquest
295882.description: A man armed with a magical bow and arrows embarks on a journey through a mystical land, joining forces with an outlaw to take down an evil witch.

307762.title: The Three Musketeers
307762.description: In this classic tale of friendship and heroism, a young, aspiring musketeer must team up with three legendary fighters to save France.

312629.title: Dragon Age Redemption
312629.description: An Elven assassin journeys to eliminate a Qunari mage with aspirations of anarchy in this fantasy series inspired by the BioWare video game.

321108.title: A Viking Saga: The Darkest Day
321108.description: While on a mission to deliver a holy text to a monastery, a novice monk is pursued by a group of ruthless Vikings who will do anything to obtain it.

341848.title: Midnight Chronicles
341848.description: In a fantastical world overwhelmed by despair, a dark priest investigates the disappearance of a cleric and uncovers a small town's forbidden legacy.

348301.title: Witchville
348301.description: A prince returns home after his father’s death and discovers he must defeat a coven of witches and their queen in order to take back his kingdom.

367685.title: Dragon Crusaders
367685.description: Fugitive knights attack a pirate ship and are cursed. To fight the curse and save they world, they must defeat the wizard-dragon responsible.

372439.title: The Crown and the Dragon: The Paladin Cycle
372439.description: A noblewoman attempts to fulfill her destiny by hiring a man to deliver her and a relic to a coronation, but a powerful enemy has other plans.

415648.title: Dragonfyre
415648.description: Unwitting Sentinel John and his soldiers must fight an army of orcs, lords of dragons and an evil sorceress hell bent on capturing a princess.

438038.title: Hammer of the Gods
438038.description: A Viking warrior journeys through hostile territory to find his banished brother and prove himself as the ruthless heir to his father's throne.

438044.title: 13 Assassins
438044.description: Thirteen heroic samurai join forces to bring down a sadistic lord and stop him from ascending the throne and plunging Japan into a war-torn future.

438052.title: Centurion
438052.description: Quintus Dias, the sole survivor of a Pictish raid, marches with General Virilus' Ninth Legion, with orders to destroy the Picts and kill their leader.

445448.title: Excalibur Kid
445448.description: After a teenage fencing enthusiast says he wishes he'd been born in medieval times, he finds himself magically transported to Camelot. There, a mysterious sorceress helps him draw the mythical "sword in the stone" and become king. But, when Zach realizes he is merely the sorceress' pawn against a young Arthur, Zach and the legendary Merlin struggle to restore history's proper timeline.

454006.title: Arthur and Merlin
454006.description: A mythic warrior, and the wizard, who mentors him along the path to the throne, fight to save the Celtic people from a druid bent on destroying them.

460977.title: Royal Deceit
460977.description: A prince’s father is murdered by his brother, who then weds his widowed mother. The prince must now discover his power to regain his rightful throne.

463724.title: Deathstalker
463724.description: A medieval muscleman sword-fights a sun lover on his way to free a princess from a wizard's castle.

465146.title: Red Sonja: Queen of Plagues
465146.description: A redheaded warrior faces impossible odds as she leads a doomed army against a fearsome opponent from her past in this animated comic.

465152.title: Sorceress
465152.description: Marked for death by their spellcasting father, twin sisters grow to become beautiful warriors who embark on a quest for vengeance.

465938.title: Mythica: The Iron Crown
465938.description: Unlikely heroes hijack a battle wagon as a wizard steals an artifact that, in the wrong hands, will flood the land with legions of the evil undead.

465939.title: Mythica: The Godslayer
465939.description: A cursed sorceress leads a quest for a weapon of the gods, but when her sworn enemy joins her she must find good within or the world will be enslaved.

466713.title: Knights of Badassdom
466713.description: A dangerous monster brings wrath, evil and destruction after three buddies take their love of live-action role playing a bit too far.

466918.title: Wizards of the Lost Kingdom
466918.description: When a treacherous sorcerer murders his father, a young wizard teams up with a heroic warrior to avenge his death and save their world.

467930.title: Arn: The Knight Templar
467930.description: As punishment for a forbidden love, a brave Swedish nobleman is sent on a treacherous journey to the Holy Land as a Knight Templar.

467936.title: Outcast
467936.description: A veteran warrior is enlisted by the children of a Chinese Emperor to overthrow their ruthless brother, who murdered their father to seize the throne.

469712.title: Dwarves of Dragon Mountain
469712.description: A sudden explosion traps four dwarfs inside treacherous Dragon Mountain. Their fight for survival begins as the miners try to dig their way out.

484792.title: Dudes and Dragons
484792.description: A brave but arrogant warrior and his estranged brother forge a quest to defeat a dragon-wielding wizard who has vowed to rid the world of love.

485300.title: Kingdom of Gladiators: The Tournament
485300.description: Fighting for a magical sword against challengers from different worlds, a Templar Knight must unite with his adversaries to battle his greedy master.

487963.title: The Legend of the Red Reaper
487963.description: A gifted and dangerous demon-woman hones her considerable skills in order to wage battle against the dark forces who betrayed her people.

489428.title: The Veil
489428.description: A deadly warrior leads a senseless tribal war until he is betrayed and left for dead. A mysterious princess heals and revives him for a final battle.

495579.title: Viking Siege
495579.description: The paths of vengeful, murderous warriors meet with demon-stalked Vikings seeking refuge with them as they’re all forced to survive a night of horror.

504927.title: The King's Guard
504927.description: A conflicted princess, torn between her heart and her father’s rule, bonds with the Captain of the King’s Guard when her castle comes under attack.

511380.title: Avenging the Throne
511380.description: Epic action film set in the late 14th century with brutal medieval face-offs as battle weary warriors find sex, sorcery, and tension in a fort refuge.

513745.title: Warrioress
513745.description: Two female warriors with exceptional fighting skills journey across a post-apocalyptic land to fight a ritual duel and fulfill an ancient prophecy.

518694.title: Merlin: The Return
518694.description: Mordred the traitor and his mother’s imprisonment for 1,500 years by Merlin may be ended by a scientist if Merlin and King Arthur don’t stop him.

518712.title: Ator: The Fighting Eagle
518712.description: A man born with a birthmark signaling his destruction of a ruling cult trains to fight the evil high priest whose minions failed to kill him at birth.

527918.title: Dark Nemesis
527918.description: In a post-apocalyptic world, desperate soldiers steal a warlord’s treasure to start anew, but must flee to a forbidden land, as assassins give chase.

528435.title: The Fellows Hip - Rise of the Gamers
528435.description: A loveable loser and his three equally geeky buddies get their first taste of belonging when a Lord of the Rings gaming competition comes to town.

528859.title: The Sorcerer's Apprentice
528859.description: An ancient world of swords and sorcery opens up for an ordinary teenage boy when he discovers his new next-door neighbor has a bent for magic.

528920.title: The Lord Protector
528920.description: Rennick, a medieval horseman, embarks on a noble quest to save the world from destructive forces and solve The Riddle of the Chosen.

530171.title: Dragon Kingdom
530171.description: To save their kingdom from a dark lord’s army, a band of warriors travels through time to fight monsters in a forbidden land and rescue their king.

530627.title: Purge of Kingdoms
530627.description: Nobles from the Eight Kingdoms make their way to 'Purge Fest 3000' hoping to end the violence between them, while the Fat King conspires against them them, in this parody.

552210.title: George and the Dragon
552210.description: When the valiant knight is asked to find a king’s lovely daughter, Sir George’s search begins, with her hunky fiance at his side and surprise ahead.

555326.title: Jabberwocky
555326.description: Monty Python's Terry Gilliam and Michael Palin reunite in this comedy adventure, when a young peasant is mistaken as a the savior against a mythical beast.

556721.title: A Viking Saga: Son of Thor
556721.description: Retribution and honor trail a Nordic boy into adulthood after his father is killed in a village massacre and he finally finds the killers years later.

563229.title: Ember Days
563229.description: In a war between spirit kingdoms, two fallen angels do battle on modern city streets and in forests, wreaking havoc to serve a Greek god and goddess.

575172.title: The Otherworld
575172.description: Celtic tale of a warrior bewitched by a fairy who takes him to a fantasy realm where they fall in love despite their existence in parallel worlds.

588235.title: The Bastard Sword
588235.description: Follow a fighter, a thief, and a hermit as they scour the forest of Soza for a magical sword rumored to give its user the ability of mind control.

588470.title: The Last King (Dubbed)
588470.description: Set in 13th century Norway, this is the tale of a great civil war in which two heroic soldiers bravely protect the last heir to the throne.

594223.title: Pungo: A Witch's Tale
594223.description: After a former Navy SEAL and a firefighter take on work as handymen in rural Virginia, they are transported into another time to save their client.

594988.title: Mythica: A Quest for Heroes
594988.description: With dreams of becoming a wizard, Marek meets a priestess and assembles a team of adventurers in an epic journey to help save her sister from an ogre.

594990.title: Mythica: The Darkspore
594990.description: When a powerful relic is stolen, Marek and her friends face a sinister new enemy in a foreign mystic bent on reclaiming the Darkspore for his master.

595005.title: Mythica: The Necromancer
595005.description: When her most loyal friend is taken hostage, Marek must embark on a corrupt mission to serve the Thieves Guild with her team of would-be heroes.

599223.title: Hercules
599223.description: The muscular Hercules performs his Labors, sails with the Argonauts, and romances the fair Iole.

604334.title: Viking Destiny
604334.description: A Viking Princess travels the world gaining wisdom and building the army she needs to win back her throne.

607993.title: The Legend Of Gobi (Dubbed)
607993.description: When a coup leaves an injured king in the desert to die, he is rescued with hopes that he might recover, correct an error, and restore his kingdom.

611206.title: The 13th Warrior
611206.description: Far from home, an exiled ambassador joins a fierce band of Viking warriors, who are attacked by ferocious creatures that devour every living thing.

612053.title: Jabberwock
612053.description: A young knight finds power in a homemade sword when he discovers that a terrifying winged dragon is out for his villagers and his beloved maiden.

612193.title: Hercules and Princess of Troy
612193.description: The heroic Hercules must do battle at Troy, along with his partners Ulysses and Diogenes, against a sea monster preying on sacrificial virgins.

613969.title: A World of Worlds
613969.description: When an evil warlock conquers her magical planet, Sofia Hayden sets out to find the legendary Royal 4 reincarnated bodies in order to take it back.

618187.title: The Ninth
618187.description: In late-19th century St. Petersburg, a young police officer investigates a string of violent murders as the new fad of spiritualism is taking root.

619676.title: Furious (English Dub)
619676.description: In 13th century Eastern Europe, the Mongul invasion of a village ends in an epic battle between seven fearless warriors and an army of thousands.

630817.title: The Rangers: Bloodstone
630817.description: When the forces of evil darken his daughter’s doorstep, an elite King's Ranger sets out on a dangerous mission to rescue her from the Outlanders.

636084.title: Age of Stone and Sky: The Sorcerer Beast
636084.description: After her tribe is destroyed by the sorcerer beast, a wandering orphan with a mysterious past discovers a powerful magic that catapults her to power.

648356.title: Boudica: Rise of the Warrior Queen
648356.description: A 16-year-old girl rejects her predetermined life and instead fights to become a warrior Queen that would lead an uprising against the might of Rome.

661916.title: Arthur & Merlin: Knights of Camelot
661916.description: In 463 AD, an older King Arthur, who has been absent for five years fighting the Romans, but must now return to Camelot and fight the corrupt Mordred.

665877.title: Season of the Witch
665877.description: Two 14th-century Crusaders are tasked with routing a suspected witch to a distant monastery to let monks determine if she caused the Black Plague.

666445.title: Spriggan
666445.description: The Ironlands is an unforgiving place. A band of swords delve into the wilderness to cleanse the impurities and rogues plaguing the indigenous people.

667184.title: Princess Cursed in Time
667184.description: Princess Elen wakes on her birthday knowing that she must solve the mystery of an evil witch's curse to save her kingdom before it is too late.

672014.title: Wolf
672014.description: A small group of Roman soldiers search for some missing warriors and realize werewolves have viciously slaughtered their missing friends.

673330.title: The Forbidden Empire
673330.description: An 18th century cartographer discovers hidden dark secrets and dangerous creatures after setting out to map the uncharted lands of Transylvania.

673676.title: Viking Quest
673676.description: Erick, a young Viking warrior, joins forces with a rival clan in order to rescue a kidnapped princess from the great Midgard Serpent.

675693.title: The Circle of Fire: The Dark Lord Kylnor
675693.description: The land is being taken over by the Dark Lord Kylnor. The people need the help of the Elves to save them.

675921.title: Magdala Rose
675921.description: In 1244, a persecuted religious sect finds refuge at the Castle of Montsegur, where a group of knights defends them from a massive crusading army.

676927.title: Sangre Vikinga (Doblado)
676927.description: Cuando un extraño se encuentra en medio de una batalla entre los dioses antiguos y los nuevos, decide que ninguno de los bandos merece ganar.

678654.title: Kingdom
678654.description: Friends fight to protect the last known dragon sanctuary from a 2000-year-old warlord who is bent on claiming the Kingdom of Britain for himself.

680202.title: Kung Fu Master (Sub Esp)
680202.description: In this action-packed martial arts film, a Shaolin monk faces deadly obstacles in his quest to destroy a violent alliance that threatens his people.

692594.title: Werewolf Castle
692594.description: After witnessing the slaughter of his loved ones, a young villager goes on a warrior’s journey with a group of Knights to end a werewolf invasion.

692600.title: Dragon Knight
692600.description: When an evil force takes hold in the Kingdom of Agonos, a knight must embark on a perilous quest to find the last dragon and save the world.

692811.title: Fengshen
692811.description: A millennia after the disappearance of the Shang Dynasty’s King’s magic pen, chaos ensues when a Tang Dynasty painter stumbles upon its whereabouts.

693752.title: Sword of God
693752.description: In the early Middle Ages, two Christian knights set off to christen a small pagan village hidden deep in the mountains where one of them will die.

693775.title: Guerrero Pagano (Doblado)
693775.description: Después de que una banda de guerreros invade un castillo, asesinando a todos a la vista, un sobreviviente invoca a una deidad pagana para vengarse.

694843.title: The Four
694843.description: A government department known as the Six Panels appoints its best officer to infiltrate a special force to stop the circulation of counterfeit money.

694853.title: God of War II
694853.description: With no memory of his past as a test subject for a ruthless imperial sorceress, the closest allies of a warlord’s general may turn out to be his foes.

698132.title: The Adventures of Maid Marian
698132.description: Upon the death of King Richard the Lionheart, Maid Marian comes out of hiding to meet Robin Hood and battle the disgraced Sheriff of Nottingham.

698700.title: Praetorian
698700.description: Set in the countryside during the height of Rome, a young couple becomes separated as a hero is sent to help fight injustice and save the innocent.

702665.title: One Warrior
702665.description: Based on a fantasy game, The One Warrior finds himself in a mythical world where he must fight many challenges to destroy the Evil Lord Shoukata.

702908.title: Thor: Thunder and Steel
702908.description: The legendary Thor is called into action when a group of religious zealots attempt to summon the Norse God of Death to conquer planet Earth.

702918.title: Viking Legacy
702918.description: A young girl and her protector at the heart of a prophecy to rule over nations must keep a magical scroll from a warlord hellbent on world domination.

707023.title: Kingslayer
707023.description: Before he ascends to be king of England, Richard the Lionheart must learn the responsibilities of leadership amidst a treacherous ambush.

707024.title: A Writer's Odyssey (Dubbed)
707024.description: Years after his child is abducted, a man is hired to kill the author of a fantasy novel, but the world of the novel seems to intersect with reality.

713124.title: Zodiac Warriors
713124.description: Twenty years after the Zodiac Warriors leader was tasked with subduing the Red Wolf, a lunar eclipse brings rumors of the chaotic creature’s return.

713151.title: The Scorpion Monster
713151.description: Two officials investigating the disappearance of Yue Ling Village at the hands of the Scorpion Demon find themselves sidelined by its own residents.

713868.title: Dragon Spell
713868.description: A journey 500 years into the past to change her father’s fate leads Sansheng to the young dragon master as a rookie and his demon-catching partner.

713869.title: Dragon Master: Dragon Hunting Squad
713869.description: A Dragon Queen’s search for the chosen one and the kidnapping of a monster hunter lead to a conspiracy that ends in a battle between good and evil.

713900.title: Venus the Cavalier
713900.description: When the parents of a commoner sought in marriage by a prince in feudal China are brutally murdered, a kung fu master takes her under his wing.

714641.title: Martial Universe 1: Immortal Stone of Nirvana
714641.description: While fighting with competitors at a kung fu gladiator contest, young hero Lin Dong is secretly targeted by various forces for the Immemorial Stone.

715982.title: Celtic Warrior: The Winter Warrior
715982.description: In the autumn of 573 AD, the civil war that divided Celtic nations in post-Roman Britain ends at the battle of Arthuet, but new raiders soon arrive.

715984.title: Celtic Warrior: Axe Raiders
715984.description: In the Highlands of Scotland during the Dark Ages when tribes fought against tribes, Fingal is avenged by his daughter Ethne in this tale of intrigue.

716243.title: The Barbarians
716243.description: In the time of dungeons, dragons and sorcery, the fate of an enslaved queen made to wed an evil ruler will one day fall in the hands of her children.

717244.title: The Sleeping Beauty
717244.description: Cursed at birth by an evil fairy, princess Anastasia gets caught in a tug of war between the fairy's sisters as they try to find a suitable antidote.

718350.title: Bluebeard
718350.description: A younger sister tells her sister about a grisly fairytale of a child bride married to an aristocratic ogre with a reputation for murdering his wives.

100000279.title: The Story of Zhan Zhao
100000279.description: This martial arts adventure based on a classic Chinese wuxia tale follows the exploits of the righteous knight errant Zhan Zhao.

100000285.title: Avengement
100000285.description: Political tensions surround the establishment of the West Factory in this action film set during the Chenghua period of the Ming Dynasty.

100000771.title: And I Was There
100000771.description: When a bickering couple gets magically transported to a fairy tale world, they undergo trials that teach them to understand what is truly valuable.

100001390.title: Tale of Tales
100001390.description: This inventive anthology film brings us three gory, gorgeous, grown-up stories of magic, monsters, and royalty based on Italian fairy tales.

100001756.title: Battle of the Dragons
100001756.description: In ancient Japan, a lord is killed and his throne stolen. Ten years later, his vengeance-seeking son meets his murderer and challenges him to a duel.

100001915.title: Dragones De Camelot (Sub Esp)
100001915.description: Después de la muerte del Rey Arturo, la malvada Morgana usa tres dragones para cazar a los restantes Caballeros de la Mesa Redonda.

100002623.title: The Emperor's Sword
100002623.description: After the emperor dies and a deranged rebel seizes power, the young daughter of a great general is all that stands between the tyrant and his quest.

100002646.title: Snow Girl and the Dark Crystal
100002646.description: Follows a fabled warrior with mysterious powers, Zhong Kui, who is forced to conquer the realms of Heaven and Hell to save his people.

100002651.title: The Thousand Faces of Dunjia
100002651.description: When an ancient creature with the power to destroy the world arises, a naive, young constable discovers a secret society with supernatural abilities.

100002689.title: The Green Knight
100002689.description: King Arthur's headstrong nephew embarks on an epic, daring quest to confront the Green Knight, a mysterious giant who appears at Camelot.

100002869.title: Battle of the Gods
100002869.description: When a ripple in spacetime transports two Viking gods and sworn enemies to the present-day world, they must rely on a young girl to get back.

0300005264.title: Conan the Adventurer
0300005264.description: Follows the thrilling exploits that pit a friendly and heroic Cimmerian-born strongman and his allies against evil wizards and sadistic villains.

0300009147.title: Merlin
0300009147.description: The legendary magician Merlin recounts the story of his war against Queen Mab and his role in the reign of King Arthur.

0300009593.title: The Slavs
0300009593.description: Draha, an ambitious young healer, finds a mysterious stranger in the woods, who she names Vlad, and helps him on his journey to remembering who he is.

0300004992.title: The Adventures of Sir Lancelot
0300004992.description: This vivid telling of the most famous Knight of the Round Table portrays his thrilling adventures serving on King Arthur’s court.

03325.title: Highlander
03325.description: As one of the immortals, entities who have waged a war between good and evil for centuries, a 400-year-old Scotsman fights for his destiny.

02166.title: Merlin
02166.description: The young wizard Merlin must keep his talent hidden in a kingdom where magic is banned as he and the future King Arthur face their destinies.

0300000011.title: Candle in the Tomb: The Lost Caverns
0300000011.description: A trio of tomb raiders explores a mysterious tomb in the Shaanxi region of China.

0300000103.title: Wu Xin: The Monster Killer 3
0300000103.description: Fed up with living, an immortal Taoist master encounters mysteries and murders and falls in love all over again while on his journey seeking death.

0300000064.title: The Immortal
0300000064.description: An immortal demon hunter and his squire team up with a parapsychologist to hunt down and defeat modern-day demons in the 21st century.
